# Python FastAPI Conventions

- Use type hints for new functions.
- Keep endpoint handlers thin; move logic to helper functions when possible.
- Validate request inputs and return clear HTTP errors.
- Preserve existing JSON contract unless user asks to change it.
- Prefer UTF-8 encoded source files.

## OCR-specific notes
- Keep per-process OCR model singleton behavior.
- For batch test features, process only pending files when required by spec.
